# Repo backend (`backend/`, Express + Prisma, port 3001).
# Local dev: leave VITE_API_BASE unset — Vite proxies /api → http://127.0.0.1:3001 when you run `cd backend && npm run dev`.
# Or set explicitly:
# VITE_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:3001
#
# Production (Vercel): set to your deployed backend/ origin (and align vercel.json /api rewrite).
# VITE_API_BASE=https://your-backend-deployment.example.com
#
# Integrations + Water Alert Evidence Packet (`/api/integrations/*`) — served from backend/src/routes/.
# VITE_DPAL_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3001
# Optional: console diagnostics for integration fetches (no secrets).
# VITE_DPAL_API_DEBUG=true
# VITE_DPAL_MEDIA_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3001
# VITE_DPAL_PUBLIC_FRONTEND_URL=https://dpal-front-end.vercel.app

# Optional: Gemini AI — browser (exposed in bundle) OR server-only:
# VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=
# Server-side Gemini: set GEMINI_API_KEY in backend/.env and on the front end:
VITE_USE_SERVER_AI=true

# Optional: Chatterbox voice id sent with TTS requests (server CHATTERBOX_VOICE_ID on backend/ is preferred).
# VITE_CHATTERBOX_VOICE_ID=positive

# Optional: OpenAI — Politician Transparency "Search & discover" query refine + Evidence workspace AI draft.
# In local dev, Vite proxies /openai-proxy so the key is not sent from browser JS (still keep key only in .env.local).
# Production: direct API calls may require a same-origin proxy if the browser blocks CORS.
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=
# VITE_OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Optional: Brave Web Search token (used for live internet search only).
# VITE_BRAVE_SEARCH_API_KEY=

# Optional: Google Maps (Locator page live map + Places autocomplete).
# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
# Optional local-only key for localhost dev (used before VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY when on localhost/127.0.0.1).
# Useful if production key is referrer-restricted and excludes localhost.
# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY_LOCAL=

# Validator Node (Verifier Action Portal — Vite app on Vercel + Reviewer API on Railway).
# Main menu navigates to this URL (same tab). Production hub dpal-front-end.vercel.app defaults to
# https://dpal-reviewer-node.vercel.app when this is unset. Override for previews or custom domains.
# VITE_VALIDATOR_PORTAL_URL=https://dpal-reviewer-node.vercel.app

# Field OS Super Agent -> Reviewer Node bridge
# Used by Request Verification Review / Refresh Review Status buttons in Field OS.
# Local default inside app (if unset): http://localhost:8787/api
# VITE_REVIEWER_NODE_API_BASE=http://localhost:8787/api

# Situation room: allow removing images from the live filing gallery (append-only audit history is kept). Staff builds only.
# VITE_INCIDENT_IMAGE_ADMIN=true

# Optional: Society Game Hub — each experience opens in a new tab when set.
# VITE_GAME_URL_INVESTIGATION_NETWORK=
# VITE_GAME_URL_INVESTIGATE_OBSERVE_INTELLIGENT=
# VITE_GAME_URL_BEACON_COMMUNITY=
# VITE_GAME_URL_CLEAN_ZONE_RESTORE_EARTH=
# VITE_GAME_URL_SAFE_REPORTING=
# VITE_GAME_URL_TAKE_THE_WALK_SHARE_MOMENT=
# VITE_GAME_URL_KITTY_COMFORT_VISITS=
# VITE_GAME_URL_SILENT_OBSERVER=
